{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.1","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:1","prev_osis_id":"Luke.014.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Paraboles de la brebis \u00e9gar\u00e9e, de la drachme perdue, de l\u2019enfant prodigue<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. Mt 9:10-13; 18:11-14.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Tous les publicains et les gens de mauvaise vie s\u2019approchaient de J\u00e9sus pour l\u2019entendre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.2","name":"Luc 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.14.35","name":"Luc 14:35","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.14.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.2","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:2","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Et les pharisiens et les scribes murmuraient, disant: Cet homme accueille des gens de mauvaise vie, et mange avec eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.3","name":"Luc 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.1","name":"Luc 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.3","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:3","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Mais il leur dit cette parabole:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.4","name":"Luc 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.2","name":"Luc 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.4","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:4","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Quel homme d\u2019entre vous, s\u2019il a cent brebis, et qu\u2019il en perde une, ne laisse les quatre-vingt-dix-neuf autres dans le d\u00e9sert pour aller apr\u00e8s celle qui est perdue, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019il la retrouve?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.5","name":"Luc 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.3","name":"Luc 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.5","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:5","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Lorsqu\u2019il l\u2019a retrouv\u00e9e, il la met avec joie sur ses \u00e9paules,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.6","name":"Luc 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.4","name":"Luc 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.6","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:6","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">et, de retour \u00e0 la maison, il appelle ses amis et ses voisins, et leur dit: R\u00e9jouissez-vous avec moi, car j\u2019ai retrouv\u00e9 ma brebis<\/span><span class=\"wj\">qui \u00e9tait perdue.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.7","name":"Luc 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.5","name":"Luc 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.7","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:7","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">De m\u00eame, je vous le dis, il y aura plus de joie dans le ciel pour un seul p\u00e9cheur qui se repent, que pour<\/span><span class=\"wj\">quatre-vingt-dix-neuf justes qui n\u2019ont pas besoin de repentance.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.8","name":"Luc 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.6","name":"Luc 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.8","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:8","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ou quelle femme, si elle a dix drachmes, et qu\u2019elle en perde une, n\u2019allume une lampe, ne balaie la maison, et ne cherche avec soin, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019elle la retrouve?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.9","name":"Luc 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.7","name":"Luc 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.9","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:9","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Lorsqu\u2019elle l\u2019a retrouv\u00e9e, elle appelle ses amies et ses voisines, et dit: R\u00e9jouissez-vous avec moi, car j\u2019ai retrouv\u00e9 la drachme que j\u2019avais perdue.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.10","name":"Luc 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.8","name":"Luc 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.10","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:10","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">De m\u00eame, je vous le dis, il y a de la joie devant les anges de Dieu pour un seul p\u00e9cheur qui se repent.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.11","name":"Luc 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.9","name":"Luc 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.11","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:11","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-32: cf. v. 1-10; 19:1-10. Mt 21:18-32. Os 14. 1 Jn 3:1. Mi 7:7, 8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Il dit encore: <span class=\"wj\">Un homme avait deux fils.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.12","name":"Luc 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.10","name":"Luc 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.12","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:12","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Le plus jeune dit \u00e0 son p\u00e8re: Mon p\u00e8re, donne-moi la part de bien qui doit me revenir. Et le p\u00e8re leur partagea son bien.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.13","name":"Luc 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.11","name":"Luc 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.13","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:13","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Peu de jours apr\u00e8s, le plus jeune fils, ayant tout ramass\u00e9, partit pour un pays \u00e9loign\u00e9, o\u00f9 il dissipa son bien en vivant dans la d\u00e9bauche.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.14","name":"Luc 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.12","name":"Luc 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.14","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:14","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Lorsqu\u2019il eut tout d\u00e9pens\u00e9, une grande famine survint dans ce pays, et il commen\u00e7a \u00e0 se trouver dans le besoin.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.15","name":"Luc 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.13","name":"Luc 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.15","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:15","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il alla se mettre au service d\u2019un des habitants du pays, qui l\u2019envoya dans ses champs garder les pourceaux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.16","name":"Luc 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.14","name":"Luc 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.16","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:16","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il aurait bien voulu se rassasier des carouges que mangeaient les pourceaux, mais personne ne lui en donnait.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.17","name":"Luc 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.15","name":"Luc 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.17","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:17","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">\u00c9tant rentr\u00e9 en lui-m\u00eame, il se dit: Combien de mercenaires chez mon p\u00e8re ont du pain en abondance, et moi, ici, je meurs de faim!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.18","name":"Luc 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.16","name":"Luc 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.18","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:18","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je me l\u00e8verai, j\u2019irai vers mon p\u00e8re, et je lui dirai: Mon p\u00e8re, j\u2019ai p\u00e9ch\u00e9 contre le ciel et contre toi,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.19","name":"Luc 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.17","name":"Luc 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.19","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:19","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">je ne suis plus digne d\u2019\u00eatre appel\u00e9 ton fils; traite-moi comme l\u2019un de tes mercenaires.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.20","name":"Luc 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.18","name":"Luc 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.20","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:20","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et il se leva, et alla vers son p\u00e8re.<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Comme il \u00e9tait encore loin, son p\u00e8re le vit et fut \u00e9mu de compassion, il courut se jeter \u00e0 son cou et le baisa.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.21","name":"Luc 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.19","name":"Luc 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.21","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:21","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Le fils lui dit: Mon p\u00e8re, j\u2019ai p\u00e9ch\u00e9 contre le ciel et contre toi, je ne suis plus digne d\u2019\u00eatre appel\u00e9 ton fils.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.22","name":"Luc 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.20","name":"Luc 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.22","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:22","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais le p\u00e8re dit \u00e0 ses serviteurs: Apportez vite la plus belle robe, et l\u2019en rev\u00eatez; mettez-lui un anneau au doigt, et des souliers aux pieds.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.23","name":"Luc 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.21","name":"Luc 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.23","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:23","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Amenez le veau gras, et tuez-le. Mangeons et r\u00e9jouissons-nous;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.24","name":"Luc 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.22","name":"Luc 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.24","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:24","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">car mon fils que voici \u00e9tait mort, et il est revenu \u00e0 la vie; il \u00e9tait perdu, et il est retrouv\u00e9. Et ils commenc\u00e8rent \u00e0 se r\u00e9jouir.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.25","name":"Luc 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.23","name":"Luc 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.25","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:25","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Or, le fils a\u00een\u00e9 \u00e9tait dans les champs. Lorsqu\u2019il revint et approcha de la maison, il entendit la musique et les danses.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.26","name":"Luc 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.24","name":"Luc 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.26","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:26","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il appela un des serviteurs, et lui demanda ce que c\u2019\u00e9tait.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.27","name":"Luc 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.25","name":"Luc 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.27","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:27","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ce serviteur lui dit: Ton fr\u00e8re est de retour, et, parce qu\u2019il l\u2019a retrouv\u00e9 en bonne sant\u00e9, ton p\u00e8re a tu\u00e9 le veau gras.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.28","name":"Luc 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.26","name":"Luc 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.28","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:28","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il se mit en col\u00e8re, et ne voulut pas entrer. Son p\u00e8re sortit, et le pria d\u2019entrer.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.29","name":"Luc 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.27","name":"Luc 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.29","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:29","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais il r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 son p\u00e8re: Voici, il y a tant d\u2019ann\u00e9es que je te sers, sans avoir jamais transgress\u00e9 tes ordres, et jamais tu ne m\u2019as donn\u00e9 un chevreau pour que je me r\u00e9jouisse avec mes amis.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.30","name":"Luc 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.28","name":"Luc 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.30","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:30","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et quand ton fils est arriv\u00e9, celui qui a mang\u00e9 ton bien avec des prostitu\u00e9es, c\u2019est pour lui que tu as tu\u00e9 le veau gras!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.31","name":"Luc 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.29","name":"Luc 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.31","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:31","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.015.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mon enfant, lui dit le p\u00e8re, tu es toujours avec moi, et tout ce que j\u2019ai est \u00e0 toi;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.32","name":"Luc 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.30","name":"Luc 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.32","label":"","reference":"Luc 15:32","prev_osis_id":"Luke.015.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.016.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.15.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">mais il fallait bien s\u2019\u00e9gayer et se r\u00e9jouir, parce que ton fr\u00e8re que voici \u00e9tait mort et qu\u2019il est revenu \u00e0 la vie, parce qu\u2019il \u00e9tait perdu et qu\u2019il est retrouv\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.15","name":"Luc 15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.16.1","name":"Luc 16:1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.16.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.15.31","name":"Luc 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.15.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc25c15d1.36337038');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc25c15d1.36337038\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc25c15d1.36337038","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.